metadata.name: A Hero's Journey
metadata.description:
Hidden deep within the mushroom forest is a dungeon unconquered by gooberkind. Legend says that within the walls of said dungeon lies the most rare of Zaza. Tales passed down from generation to generation say that one puff from this rarest of herbs will enlighten the user to the level of the celestials, overcome them with immense euphoria, and bestow upon them an insurmountable amount of rizz!  

Many a goober have tried their hand at tackling the dungeon for just a mere whiff of the zaza, but none have ever conquered the many challenges hidden within. 

Our hero stands before of the mighty doors of the Dungeon. Determined to be the first of any goober to not only get a puff of the ever so sought for Zaza, but to also bring the herb home to puff, puff, and pass with their friends! 

Let our adventure BEGIN!
